article.headline: Byron Ireland scores 15 as Nicholls eases past Mississippi College 79-35
article.description: — Byron Ireland scored 15 points to lead Nicholls to a 79-35 victory over Mississippi College on Monday night.
article.linkText: Byron Ireland scores 15 as Nicholls eases past Mississippi College 79-35
article.story: THIBODAUX, La. -- — Byron Ireland scored 15 points to lead Nicholls to a 79-35 victory over Mississippi College on Monday night. Ireland also added five rebounds for the Colonels (3-4). Michael Gray Jr. scored 14 points, going 3 of 5 from the floor, including 2 for 4 from 3-point range, and 6 for 8 from the line. Mekhi Collins shot 6 of 7 from the field to finish with 12 points. Tyree Bracey finished with 11 points and seven rebounds to pace the Choctaws. Tyshun Briscoe added eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
